{
  "sections": {
    "gp_section_566798216318682049": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "7dd022ba927f82e839c67bba9b18ed786a180a9b88520485b6cc728a1f29bb1b_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg5A_s7vPft_text": "<p>From the moment they slip it on, they know it’s different. <strong>There’s a rhythm to the way it works.</strong> A calm that sets in. A feeling of lightness that wasn’t there before.</p>",
        "gg6lqX8ncBw_text": "Backed by Physical Therapists. Grounded in Real Science.",
        "gg9L3EDUCMV_text": "Loved by Our Customers for a Reason",
        "ggGQXnMY5zT_text": "Loved by Our Customers for a Reason",
        "ggHXNK0bxqW_text": "<p><a href=\"* https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/39222789/\"><u>*https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/39222789/</u></a></p>",
        "ggL4iNUkg4Z_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-3236e293-92c7-4b9b-8e31-fb0dae6327de.png",
        "ggTX3oVSncW_text": "<p>Additionally, research indicates that IPC can alleviate muscle soreness and expedite recovery by <strong>promoting blood flow</strong> and facilitating the <strong>removal of metabolic waste.</strong>**</p>",
        "ggWaM2WXPMT_text": "<p><a href=\"** https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1360859224005813\"><u>**https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1360859224005813</u></a></p>",
        "ggaFHF5sugD_text": "<p>It’s become the thing they reach for after a long day, after hours of standing, or whenever that heavy, swollen feeling returns.</p>",
        "ggbeYBd0f0Y_text": "<p><strong>Once they feel the relief</strong>, they never want to go back.</p>",
        "ggcllM8jPEK_text": "<p>By integrating this clinically validated technology into a user-friendly, at-home device, SmoothSpine™ offers a convenient solution for individuals <strong>seeking relief from leg discomfort and swelling.</strong></p>",
        "ggfu54xW6VT_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-983f6c08-f3ef-4b98-a7bd-c00ed23a678f.png",
        "ggiVlsgDWSA_text": "<p>The SmoothSpine™ 3-in-1 Leg Massager is grounded in the same <strong>pneumatic compression therapy</strong> utilized in medical settings to treat conditions like edema and lymphedema. Clinical studies have demonstrated the effectiveness of IPC in reducing leg swelling, enhancing ankle mobility, and <strong>improving overall quality of life</strong> for patients with limited mobility.*</p>",
        "ggihBBrHnWy_text": "<p>People aren’t just using the SmoothSpine™ 3-in-1 Leg Massager - they’re building it into their daily routine.</p>",
        "ggihisY810h_text": "Backed by Physical Therapists. Grounded in Real Science."
      },
      "type": "gp-section-566798216318682049"
    },
    "gp_section_566798216318747585": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "57f80c7cd01507312ff68fd3dbbbaeac7f64fd2a61acc06acdfeb54ca3c84772_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg5779-Q2LD_text": "<p>Yes, and we recommend it! Just 15 minutes a day can help reduce swelling and improve comfort over time.</p>",
        "ggBJa8Yn5GB_text": "Frequently Asked Questions",
        "ggGBgdMGN1b_text": "<p>Absolutely. It comes with adjustable straps and extra velcro extensions to comfortably fit a wide range of leg sizes.</p>",
        "ggJ59b-ywE__text": "<p>It uses gentle air compression to mimic the natural pumping action of your calf muscles - boosting circulation, reducing swelling, and relieving tension in your lower legs and feet.</p>",
        "ggOF78_pLax_text": "<p>Yes! The device was specifically designed for people with swelling, edema, or circulation issues. It’s noninvasive, drug-free, and easy to control.</p>",
        "ggUxWA6ILkw_text": "<p>Each session takes about 15 minutes - just enough to give your legs a break and help them feel lighter again.</p>",
        "ggZ3I5t3Bhg_text": "<p>Nope. You can use it while sitting on the couch, watching TV, or lying in bed. It works while you rest.</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_0": "<p>How does the SmoothSpine™ 3-in-1 Leg Massager work?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_1": "<p>Is it safe for older adults or people with poor circulation?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_2": "<p>Will it fit my legs?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_3": "<p>Can I use it every day?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_4": "<p>Do I need to stand or move while using it?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_5": "<p>How long does each session take?</p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-566798216318747585"
    },
    "gp_section_566798216318813121": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "cf41740c47586d85eaac8d31b98436967f384be4d0ac9dacaaa71fbb92c24bee_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg9sfrUDNiv_text": "Gentle Compression. Powerful Results.",
        "ggFoLsfJU5j_text": "<p>The SmoothSpine™ 3-in-1 Leg Massager uses <strong>gentle air pressure</strong> to rhythmically squeeze and release your legs - just like your muscles do when you walk. This natural pumping motion <strong>helps boost circulation, reduce swelling</strong>, and flush out the fluid that builds up in your lower legs and feet.</p>",
        "ggNDYVqN7Gc_text": "Gentle Compression. Powerful Results.",
        "ggNxAHEd9SQ_text": "<p>It’s designed to be easy: just wrap it around your legs, choose your settings, and relax. No effort. No learning curve. Just <strong>quiet, consistent relief </strong>that gets better the more you use it.&nbsp;</p>",
        "gguTWvepLsf_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-04fc00b8-a35a-437c-a714-02c9a588391c.png"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-566798216318813121"
    },
