        "ggnO_gdadKG_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:18px;\">We stand by the quality of every SmoothSpine™ 3-in-1 Leg Massager. Each device is carefully tested and built to deliver reliable relief, session after session.</span></p>",
