        "gg4lOxj8MET_text": "<p>“I Thought It’d Be Complicated - It’s Not”</p>",
        "ggBi7vQvbIj_text": "<p>“I Can’t Exercise Much, So This Changed Everything”</p>",
        "ggJ8hCrLXJq_text": "<p>“I’ve always been told to “just move more” to help my circulation, but my swollen feet made walking almost impossible some days. This ™ 3-in-1 Leg Massager was the first thing that helped without hurting. It mimics movement without the strain. I use it every night now and wake up without that tight, heavy feeling in my legs.”</p>",
