        "ggmciU_MO8m_text": "<p>– Mark Turner, Verified Purchase</p>",
        "ggnkoHZd9S5_text": "<p>“I’ve tried everything- compression socks, soaking my feet, even prescription meds. Nothing ever helped the swelling down. I was skeptical about this 3-in-1 Leg Massager, but I’m so glad I gave it a chance. After a week of daily use, I could finally fit into my sneakers comfortably again. My legs feel lighter, and I actually enjoy using it.”</p>",
