        "ggLpJvHJ_hk_text": "<p><strong>It’s like a gentle workout for your legs… without any effort!</strong></p>",
        "ggaZ6vzwlyO_text": "<p>This simple action supports better circulation, reduces fluid buildup, and relieves that heavy, aching feeling - all while you sit back and relax.</p>",
