        "ggV2Gzg1kTE_text": "<p>Susan M.</p>",
        "ggavmk0YmvV_text": "<p>Tired of swollen, heavy legs that hurt no matter what you do?</p>",
        "ggbcW1KUC8b_text": "<p>Improves blood flow in your legs</p>",
